projects.name: Todo Project
projects.description: A simple todo application built using React. Allows users to create, edit, and delete tasks. Styled with CSS for a clean interface.

projects.name: E-commerce Website
projects.description: An online shopping platform with cart functionality, developed using React, Redux, Node.js, and MongoDB. Supports user authentication and order management.

projects.name: Weather App
projects.description: A weather application to check current weather conditions. Provides detailed weather forecasts based on user location using React and OpenWeatherMap API.

projects.name: Blog Website
projects.description: A platform for creating and sharing blog posts. Includes user authentication, comment sections, and post management. Built with React, Redux, Express, and MongoDB.

projects.name: Portfolio Website
projects.description: A personal portfolio showcasing projects and skills. Features project galleries, skill showcases, and contact form. Designed using React and styled with Tailwind CSS.

moreProjects.name: Recipe App
moreProjects.description: Discover and save favorite recipes. Built with React, Firebase, and Spoonacular API.

moreProjects.name: Fitness Tracker
moreProjects.description: Track fitness activities and progress. Built with React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.

moreProjects.name: E-learning Platform
moreProjects.description: Online learning platform with courses, quizzes, and progress tracking. Developed using React, Redux, Django, and PostgreSQL.

moreProjects.name: Chat Application
moreProjects.description: Real-time chat application for communication between users. Built with React, Socket.IO, and Node.js.
